### Summary

**9 of 10 tests** are either assertion-free or use only `IsNotNull` — the weakest possible assertion. This suite gives the illusion of coverage while verifying almost zero business logic. The highest-risk gaps are `UpdatePrice`, `ApplyBulkDiscount`, and `ImportFromCsv` — all contain branching/transformation logic that is completely unverified.
